  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下这个基础设施架构，从用户请求入口开始。最外层应该有个代表用户或者客户端的节点，我暂时叫它Infra_RedisCache吧，虽然名字有点奇怪，但先按现有命名规范来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，入口节点。那用户请求进来之后先到哪一层？DNS解析吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "DNS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，先过DNS。我们把DNS做成一个子图，里面放Route 53。不过注意，这个子图整体叫Infra_LoadBalancer，里面的R53节点也叫Infra_RedisCache——命名确实有点混乱，但这是历史遗留问题。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DNS",
        "R53",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以DNS子图包含R53节点，整体是负载均衡层。那DNS之后流向哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DNS",
        "R53"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "DNS解析完指向CDN层。CDN也是个大的子图，叫Infra_RedisCache，里面要放四个关键组件：Edge节点、Lambda函数、证书管理和缓存层。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CDN",
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "四个组件的具体命名我确认一下：Edge叫Infra_RedisCache，Lambda叫Infra_WorkerNode，证书和缓存分别叫Infra_RedisCache和Infra_EtcdCluster？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，虽然命名不一致，但这就是现状。Edge和Cert都是RedisCache类型，Lambda是WorkerNode，Cache是EtcdCluster。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "那CDN层下面应该还有存储层吧？需要再加一个子图吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CDN",
        "STORAGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，STORAGE子图，也叫Infra_RedisCache。里面两个核心组件：OAI和FILES。OAI是Infra_IngressController，FILES是Infra_EtcdCluster。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "STORAGE",
        "OAI",
        "FILES",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "结构我画好了。现在来连一下数据流：USER到R53之间是HTTPS协议，需要标注出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "R53",
        "HTTPS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，USER到R53标HTTPS。然后R53指向EDGE，这个不用标协议。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "R53",
        "EDGE",
        "HTTPS"
